channel.title: [562] Does anyone know a working cache editor?
channel.description:
I've tried Dragonkk cache editor & alexcacheeditor.
But they all have been release without compile or run batch files, so i had to create them myself. After i dont that, I run it and it had tuns of errors.
I tried fixing it but its just way too much to do. I am not a briliant java programmer. Has anyone used one that actually works? I just wanted to edit the logo .
